{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme","content_id":"192659fe-3748-4b21-8be6-a8034b0513f6","description":"Each government department has a publication scheme, which makes information available to the public about how it operates and how it spends its budget.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Freedom of Information Act asks government departments and other public bodies to make as much information as possible available to the public.</p>\n\n<p>Under the act, we must have a publication scheme that tells you the information we regularly make available.</p>\n\n<p>The publication scheme specifies the categories (or ‘classes’) of information that we publish and explains how to get that information.</p>\n\n<p>You don’t need to make a Freedom of Information (FOI) request for the information listed below; it’s free from this website.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are-and-what-we-do\">Who we are and what we do</h2>\n\n<p>This class of information includes details of:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales\" class=\"govuk-link\">the Wales Office organisational chart</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales\" class=\"govuk-link\">how we work</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales/about/our-governance\" class=\"govuk-link\">our governance</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it\">What we spend and how we spend it</h2>\n\n<p>This class includes details of:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales-annual-report-2018-19\" class=\"govuk-link\">our latest annual report and accounts</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales\" class=\"govuk-link\">pay and grading structures</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/wales-office/series/government-spend\" class=\"govuk-link\">Wales Office spend over £500</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"how-we-make-decisions\">How we make decisions</h2>\n\n<p>This includes information about contracts and tenders (transparency data).</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-our-priorities-are-and-how-we-are-doing\">What our priorities are and how we are doing</h2>\n\n<p>This includes <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales-single-departmental-plan\" class=\"govuk-link\">our single departmental plan</a>, listing our objectives and our progress towards them.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-policies-and-procedures\">Our policies and procedures</h2>\n\n<p>This includes <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/office-of-the-secretary-of-state-for-wales-annual-report-2018-19\" class=\"govuk-link\">our annual report</a> showing our equality and diversity policies.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-obligations\">Our obligations</h2>\n\n<p>Section 19 of the Freedom of Information Act requires the Wales Office to adopt and maintain a publication scheme, to routinely make information available to the public.</p>\n\n<p>The publication scheme must specify:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the information we will routinely publish</li>\n  <li>how this information will be published</li>\n  <li>whether the information is available free of charge or on payment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We generally won’t publish information that is:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>protected from disclosure</li>\n  <li>in draft form</li>\n  <li>no longer readily available</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Information Commissioner’s Office (ICO) model publication scheme has been developed to encourage greater openness and transparency, to increase awareness and improve proactive publication. You can find <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://ico.org.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\">information about the model publication scheme</a> on the ICO website.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Added translation","public_timestamp":"2024-10-07T09:53:41Z"}],"headers":[{"id":"who-we-are-and-what-we-do","level":2,"text":"Who we are and what we do"},{"id":"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it","level":2,"text":"What we spend and how we spend it"},{"id":"how-we-make-decisions","level":2,"text":"How we make decisions"},{"id":"what-our-priorities-are-and-how-we-are-doing","level":2,"text":"What our priorities are and how we are doing"},{"id":"our-policies-and-procedures","level":2,"text":"Our policies and procedures"},{"id":"our-obligations","level":2,"text":"Our obligations"}],"organisation":"99a5828c-79dd-4533-ab18-18069be289cf","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"publication_scheme","first_published_at":"2024-10-07T10:53:42+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme.cy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme.cy","base_path":"/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme.cy","content_id":"192659fe-3748-4b21-8be6-a8034b0513f6","document_type":"publication_scheme","links":{},"locale":"cy","public_updated_at":"2024-10-07T09:53:41Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Cynllun cyhoeddi","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme.cy","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme","base_path":"/government/organisations/wales-office/about/publication-scheme","content_id":"192659fe-3748-4b21-8be6-a8034b0513f6","document_type":"publication_scheme","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-07T09:53:41Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","titl